{"tid":691682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實幼稚唔係問題(月經屌連登post)","createTime":"2018-06-06T03:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:47:29.000Z","uid":173852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b60abb51e94e336c475765ac59e44220f02af1c","tid":691682,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"近排係連登討論好電影，講幾套好野，即刻就有人話咩「垃圾」,「懶高檔」<br />\n傾漫畫，講到龍珠，即係有人跳出黎話咩故事畫工垃圾<br />\n跟住波台咩玩具又盛<br />\n<br />\n依類回覆有一個共通點，就係純粹拋出黎引人扯火，根本無解釋無理由，算唔得上討論<br />\n波台果類玩野台唔講啦 但傾下電影/漫畫都咁真係好撚無癮<br />\n<br />\n講真，幼稚其實唔係問題，只要真係有心討論，其實耐心d同你傾有咩問題？但懶係有見地，一出聲就想話比人聽自己有幾醒幾撚獨特。成日申自己溝唔到女，連基本既待人接物都可以玩到咁乞人憎，咁抵仆街啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6353188ed68c2eb23f78555763d266dbf22d2a","tid":691682,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5025f7929e3312ce3354acff4801db4d5d58beac","tid":691682,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6353188ed68c2eb23f78555763d266dbf22d2a","tid":691682,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:44:40.000Z","msg":"唔止錯別字<br />\n連meme都要反<br />\n肥絲你不如去北韓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8574e6877ef8001b61a1dde7b373f1bcb7eb005b","tid":691682,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c40f8617a7e3c3605356f3d0c6470072a2050c27","tid":691682,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6353188ed68c2eb23f78555763d266dbf22d2a","tid":691682,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"咁點改好丫肥絲老師"}]}